From Andy Woodward Subject re Its still cold first ride of the One thing is certain though its still too After about minutes I had to stop and hold my muffler for a When I got home after a few hours I kept all my gear on for about a half hour in the humidity no wind protection and do not mix Hell This is I retired my fleece from under the Aerostich last month when the temperature got aboce Try living a couple of years on the dole so you cant afford any You put the gear on in October abd you take it off again in Getting out on the bike seems like a luxury in comparison cos oyur usuallu going somewhere Its all Happy cold Who are you trying to kid its the pain that makes it all